content: Name 7 actors and/or actresses who were considered members of the "brat pack" in the 1980s.

chosen:
The Brat Pack was a group of young actors and actresses who were popular in the 1980s. Here are seven members of the Brat Pack:

- Rob Lowe
- Emilio Estevez
- Andrew McCarthy
- Demi Moore
- Molly Ringwald
- Ally Sheedy
- John Cusack
rejected: Rob Lowe, Emilio Estevez, Andrew McCarthy, Demi Moore, Molly Ringwald, Ally Sheedy, and Judd Nelson.
